WEBVTT

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:02.976
"Remarkably like that of the flowers
of the Spanish chestnut.

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:04.976
Sometimes quite freshly floral,

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:07.048
and then again sometimes
extremely pungent."

00:06:07.072 --> 00:06:11.976
(Laughter)

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:16.976
Okay. In 1999, in the state of Israel,
a man began hiccupping.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:19.976
And this was one of those cases
that went on and on.

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:22.000
He tried everything his friends suggested.

00:06:22.024 --> 00:06:23.976
Nothing seemed to help.

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.422
Days went by.

00:06:25.446 --> 00:06:29.976
At a certain point, the man,
still hiccupping, had sex with his wife.

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:31.976
And lo and behold, the hiccups went away.